1. Get the hold of controller object.
2. Get the frame object by callin controller.frame (or sth like that).
3. Use ScreenTapGesture to register the key taps.
4. Use Position property of ScreenTapGesture to determine the place where the tap occurred.
5. Step 4 returns the Vector object (x,y,z). y is upwards.
6. Somehow use Vector or properties of ScreenTapGesture to determine the strength of the tap.
7. Play the correct note of the length depending on the tap strength.
8. Try to implement the proccessing of multiple taps.
